      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup by analyst not involved in original build; checklist-based review documented.",
      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed by independent FDA analyst using ASME V&V 40 checklist. Boundary conditions, contact definitions, and material assignments confirmed correct. Two minor annotation errors corrected prior to final run; no substantive modeling errors identified."
