      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled and tested (Lab 1: n=6, Lab 2: n=5). All screws and rods sourced from same production lot (Lot 2021-DPS-7p5). Sample size sufficient to estimate mean and standard deviation for acceptance metric computation."
    },
    {
