      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span at least two clinically relevant load magnitudes or configurations to assess model extrapolation.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (35 mm offset, compression-bending only). Torsion and tension-bending configurations not tested. Achieved level 1 because only one test condition was evaluated; required level 2 for medium model risk. This gap is acknowledged and flagged in the decision record."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
