      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative acceptance metric E/uval < 1.96 for all three QoIs; percent difference < 10%.",
      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy both acceptance criteria. E/uval values: 1.31, 1.74, 1.58. Percent differences: 4.2%, 6.8%, 5.5%. Validation uncertainty uval computed from experimental repeatability and model numerical uncertainty combined in quadrature."
